n = int(input())
    graph = [[] for i in range(n)]
    for i in range(n-1):
        a, b = map(int, input().split())
        graph[a-1].append(b-1)
        graph[b-1].append(a-1)
    v = list(map(int, input().split()))
    v.insert(0, 0)
    visited = [False] * n
    visited[0] = True
    q = [0]
    ans = 0
    while q:
        cur = q.pop(0)
        for i in graph[cur]:
            if not visited[i]:
                visited[i] = True
                q.append(i)
                ans += abs(v[cur] - v[i])
                v[i] = v[cur]
    print(ans)
